\id 2TI - Bekwel Bible
\h Mɛkana ɛ Pɔl, yii bhɔɔba pɛ daa Timote
\toc3 2Tm
\toc2 Timote yii Bɔɔba
\toc1 Mɛkana ɛ Pɔl yii Bhɔɔba, pɛ daa Timote
\mt2 Mɛkana ɛ Pɔl, yii bhɔɔba pɛ daa Timote
\mt1 Timote Bɔɔba
\imt1 Ɛniel
\ip Mɛkana mɛ mɛmbá nakyeeda nɛ Timote ɛ, ye nabɛ ɛ́ lwomel e mɛsik mɛ mot-lwoma Pɔl, nyɛy e membok (\xt 2.9\xt*), ye nabɛ ɛ́ mbula bot nabet nyɛ (\xt 1.15; 4.10-16\xt*). Eghɛŋ tak, nyɛ nabɛ ɛ́ nyɛ eezenaagu náá, nyɛ moo aagwyɛ (\xt 4.6\xt*). Nyɛ naamwana nɛ Timote mot nadi egyee nɛ nɛ tɔ mɛsa ɔ, mot nyɛ nadi ekwyɛl dáa mɔn ɔ.
\ip Mɛkana mak kaadaa ɛ tsik ɛ Pɔl: étɛp mɛsa mɛ dáa mot lwoma, mɛlyo mɛ, mezuk mɛ kɔ ɛsu ɛ Mbɛɛ Bhaadal. Pɔl ɛpedjɛ mɛlyo nɛ Timote. Nyɛ ɛpedjɛ nyɛ mɛghaaz náá, nyɛ waaboma nɛ mezuk kɔ ɛsu ɛ mɛsa mɛ Klisto (\xt 2.1-13\xt*). Bhii tak, nyɛ ɛpebaalɛɛ náá, nyɛ goola ɛnyɔɛpe mɛkpa mɛ Zɛɛb (\xt 2.14—4.15\xt*). Dum nɛ tɛp tak ɛ, Timote goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛkaab ɛni tɔ bɛ mɛwɔ, ɛlum koŋ nɛ bot ɛ mesyem, ɛbaŋa mɛfulu mɛ Pɔl. Ɛsok nɛ etɛp djas, nyɛ goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛdi sosoob nɛ mɛlyo mɛ Pɔl nɛ yii bɛdhiiti bɛlyoel ekeletyɛ nalyo nyɛ ɛ́.
\ip Bhis eboo bɛtyaasɛs ɛ Yezu aagwyɛ ɛ́, bot ɛ nadjila bɛ e mɛsa mɛ etyaasɛs ɔ, nabaazokɛ ɛ dáa bɔɔ. Ye ɛ́ deenek ɛ, \em bɛ nabaal ɛnyɔɛpe mɛkpa\em* mɛ bɛ nagwak nɛ bɛlyoel bɔɔ ɛ. Tin, bɛ baagoka ɛ nɛ ɛlaa bɛmɛkana mɛ na Dɛɛ. Eghɛŋ Pɔl nakwyal Timote bɛmɛkana ɛ, e sok tak, bɛmɛkana mɛ tak nadi ɛ́, yii Ɛbhɛŋ ɛ Namwa, nɛghu ba bɛdhiiti bɔɔ epes mɛkana mɛ Ɛbhɛŋ ɛ na Bes. Ekwyala bak djas ɛ «nɛ boo mɛtaŋ étɛp ɛlyo bot etsɛɛtsɛ, étɛp ɛsa náá bot myaal, étɛp ɛkoobal embee mɛsa mɔɔ, étɛp ɛsa náá mot di nɛ tsik epiki» (\xt 3.16\xt*).
\c 1
\s1 Mɛswosel
\p 
\v 1 Ye ɛ́ mam, Pɔl mot-lwoma ɛ Yezu Klisto tɔ ɛkwosak ɛ Zɛɛb, mɛ ɛ́ wak ɛ étɛp ɛgoola bin tsik. Ye ɛ́ tsik Zɛɛb edjɛ mena kɔ ɛsu ɛgwakel ɛ lena nɛ Yezu Klisto.
\v 2 Mɛ kwyal mɛkana mak ɛ nɛ wɔy Timote mɔn'am mɛ di ekwyɛl ɔ: beta náá, enɛm nɛ embɛɛ, nɛ lyem ghoŋ, nɛ egwyem ɛ Zɛɛb sɛɛg bɛ nɛ Yezu Klisto di nɛ nɔ.
\s1 Pɔl ɛpeghaapɛɛ Zɛɛb kɔ ɛsu ɛ Timote
\p 
\v 3 Mɛ ɛpeghaapɛɛ Zɛɛb mot mɛ di esa mɛsa mɛ nɛ lyem wat dáa bɛbhaab'am nasa ɛ. Mwos nɛ pum e sok mɛ di edjaala Zɛɛb ɛ, mɛ nɛ dyeebadjaala étɛp'ɔ.
\v 4 Mɛ ɛpetaala meŋal mɔ, e di'enek, mɛ ɛ́ nɛ gwyes ɛbee wɔ étɛp lyem'am neelwood nɛ mɛmyaala.
\v 5 Mɛ ɛpebaataala dɔɔ nɛ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb, wɔ zedum nɛ lyem wat ɛ. Ye ɛ́ kɔkɔ mbi ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb yii naye yɔ Loyis nɛ nyoog Enis nadi nɛ ye ɛ́. Mɛ eemyal náá, kɔkɔ mbi ɛdum ɛ koŋ ɛlenek ɛ tɔ lɔ.
\s1 Zuka nɛ nam kɔ ɛsu ɛ mbɛɛ Bhaadal
\p 
\v 6 Ye ɛ́ étɛp tak ɛ mɛ baadi elɛɛ nɛ nɔ náá, baawyɛl mɛgoo mɛ ɛkɛɛ ɛ Zɛɛb nadjɛ wɔ ɛ, e sok mɛ nakɛl wɔ mɛmbɔ ɛ.
\v 7 Etɛɛ náá, Sisim Zɛɛb nadjɛ mena ɛ, ye nabɛ ɛ́ ààbɛ etɛɛ náá mena di bɛtyak-bel, ye ɛ́ Sisim ghwyil, yii kwyɛl nɛ yii ɛdil ɛ lyem.
\p 
\v 8 Sa wɔ ààdi nɛ syen ɛgoola Mbɛɛ Bhaadal ɛ Ghɛŋ'enaka. Sa wɔ ààbaadi nɛ syen nɛ nam, mot di kwom kɔ ɛsu ɛ lɛ ɔ. Deenek, myaala ɛzuk sama nɛ nam étɛp Mbɛɛ Bhaadal. Tin, dia nɛ ɛbwaalel nɛ ghwyil Zɛɛb di edjɛ mena ɛ.
\v 9 Nyɛy ɛ́ natsik mena, nɛ ɛsa náá mena dika bot ɛ́ dhaad mbyak'ɛ. Ye nabɛ ɛ́ ààbɛ kɔ ɛsu ɛ enɛm esa bena, ye nabɛ ɛ́ egeka bɛ met nɛ enɛm nɛ embee bɛ met. Tin, Zɛɛb naadjɛ mena enɛm nɛ embɛɛ binek e ze ɛ Yezu Klisto, ɛsok nɛ nyɛ nɛkus bhwak.
\v 10 Tin, ɛkɛɛ enɛm nɛ embɛɛ tak kazɛnyen mos ɛ e ɛtuula ɛ mɛtsik-bot menaka Yezu Klisto. Nyɛy ɛ mot nakwak ɛsyee ɔ, dum nɛ Mbɛɛ Bhaadal ɛ nyɛ natel mena tsik na kɔm-kɔm.
\v 11 Zɛɛb naadjɛ mɛ mɛsa mɛ ɛdi mot-lwoma nɛ lyoel, étɛp ɛkɛgoola Mbɛɛ Bhaadal.
\v 12 Kɔ ɛsu ɛ tak ɛ, mɛ di ebee mezuk mɛ mɛ di ezuk'aak. Mɛ tok nɛ syen étɛp tak etɛɛ náá, mɛ nɛ gu mot mɛ wa ɛbwaalel ɛ lam nɛ nɔ ɛnyɔɛpe. Tin, mɛ ɛpemyaal náá, Zɛɛb ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil ɛbaal sa nyɛ nadjɛ mɛ ɛ kɛkum dwoo epɛɛ ɛ.
\v 13 Deenek, mɛkpa mɛ etsɛɛtsɛ wɔ nagwak nɛ nam ɛ, ye ɛ́ di mɛkpa mɛfulu mɛ tsik'ɔ. Tin, pyeta tɔ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb, kwyɛla bot nɛ kwyɛl di edus pɛ daa Yezu Klisto ɛ.
\v 14 Deenek, baala mbɛɛ mɛlyo djas nazedjɛaa wɔ nɛ ghwyil Sisim na Dɛɛ di tɔ lena ɛ.
\s1 Esosoob ɛ Onezifɔɔd nɛ yii bot ɛ mɛbyel mɛ
\p 
\v 15 Wɔ nɛ gu náá bot ɛ kyee dik Azi djas naazekaab mɛ, tɔ sama bot ɛ tak, ye nabɛ ɛ́ nɛ Fizɛl bɛ nɛ Elmozɛn.
\v 16 Beta náá, Ghɛŋ sa enɛm esa bɛ nɛ bot ɛ mɛbyel ɛ Onezifɔɔd, etɛɛ náá, nyɛ naadyeebadjɛ mɛ mɛghaaz. Tin, nyɛ nabɛ ɛ́ ààgwak syen nɛ nam, mam mot membok.
\v 17 Deenek, dáa nyɛ tuula tɔ ghaada Lɔm ɛ, nyɛ naawa zii e ɛsaa mɛ, kɛbela mɛ.
\v 18 Tin, beta náá, Ghɛŋ sa enɛm esa e Zɛɛb nɛ nɛ dwoo epɛɛ. Wɔy ɛmet nɛ baagu ɛnyɔɛpe esa djas nyɛ nasa nɛ nam pɛ kyee dik Efɛɛz ɛ.
\c 2
\s1 Mɛlyo dum nɛ dáa mot di egoka nɛ ɛdi mbɛɛ sodja ɛ Klisto ɛ
\p 
\v 1 Wɔy, mɔn'am, dia nɛ ghwyil tɔ enɛm nɛ embɛɛ di edus pɛ daa Yezu Klisto ɛ.
\v 2 Mɛlyo mɛ wɔ nadi egwak mɛ egoola e mis mɛ bɛtɛ nɛ bɛtyaasɛs ɛ. Deenek, lyoa yɛ nɛ bɛtɛtɛ ɛ bot, bot aadi nɛ ghwyil ɛ aabaalyo bɛdhiiti bot ɔ.
\p 
\v 3 Zuka nɛ nam dhatyee tɛtɛ sodja ɛ Yezu Klisto.
\v 4 Mot di náá, nyɛ dinaa kuku ɛsa mɛsa mɛ esodja ɔ, nyɛ kwyɛl náá, kukuma yɛ myaala nɛ nɛ ɔ, sa nyɛ ààbaasa dhiiti mɛsa mɛ sis.
\v 5 Ye ɛ́ tyee wat mot di esa mɛbhoola tɔ mɛsɛŋ mɛ ɛwyis ɛ kaab ɔ. Nyɛ aabela efute ɛ, nyɛ sa dáa mɛtiŋ mɛ mɛbhoola mɛ tak di elɛɛ ɛ.
\v 6 Beeka mbɛel mɛbhek di ezuk ɛlyelɛpe tɔ mɛsa mɛ pyeeb'ɛ ɔ. Nyɛ goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛdi mot mɛkɛn aadɛ esa nyɛ nabɛ ɛ.
\v 7 Simza ɛnyɔɛpe sa mɛ di elɛɛ wɔ ɛ, deenek, Ghɛŋ ɛwaasa náá wɔ mɛt etɛp djas.
\s1 Taala Yezu Klisto mot nagom ɔ
\p 
\v 8 Taala nɛ Yezu Klisto, dha ɛ Dhavid mot nagom bhis ɛsyee ɔ, dáa Mbɛɛ Bhaadal mɛ di egoola ɛ di elɛɛ.
\v 9 Ye ɛ́ kɔ ɛsu ɛ Mbɛɛ Bhaadal'ak ɛ mɛ di ezuk, kɔ ɛsu ɛ tak ɛ mɛ di kɔɔla, dáa mot di esa embee étɛp ɔ. Tin, mɛkpa mɛ Zɛɛb tok kɔɔla!
\v 10 Etɛp tak ɛ mɛ di emaad etɛp djas kɔ ɛsu ɛ bot ɛ Zɛɛb nazesɛɛ ɔ. Mɛ sa deenek ɛ etɛɛ náá, bot ɛ Zɛɛb nazesɛɛ ɔ, neebela tsik nɛ duu na kɔm-kɔm di edus pɛ daa Yezu Klisto ɔ.
\v 11 Ye ɛ́ mbɛɛ mɛ mɛkpa mɛ etsɛɛtsɛ:
\q1 «Mena gwyɛka sama wat nɛ Klisto ɔɔ,
\q1 mena waadika nɛ tsik sama wat nɛ nɛ.
\q1 
\v 12 Mena pyetka ɔɔ,
\q1 mena waakɛ sama nɛ nɛ.
\q1 Mena byenka nyɛ ɔɔ,
\q1 nyɛy pe aabyen mena.
\q1 
\v 13 Mena di ààdika sosoob ɔɔ, nyɛy ɛ́ aazodiɛ sosoob,
\q1 etɛɛ náá, nyɛy tok nɛ ghwyil ɛswonal mɛkpa mɛ nuub'ɛ\x - \xo 2:13 \xt Ɛla 23.19.\x*.»
\s1 Mot-mɛsa mɛ Zɛɛb di ekwyɛl ɔ
\p 
\v 14 Baagheelelɛɛ etɛp bak nɛ bot, dula bɛ mɛlo e mis ɛ Zɛɛb náá, sa bɛ ààsuu mɛso kɔ ɛsu ɛ mɛkpa. Ɛsuu mɛso menek ɛ ààval sa wat, mbi yenek e saŋ ɛ ɛsaab esisim e bot ɛ di egwak ɔ.
\v 15 Saŋa náá, wɔ di piki e mis ɛ Zɛɛb, dáa mot-mɛsa di ààbɛ nɛ syen e ɛgoola ɛnyɔɛpe Mbɛɛ Bhaadal etsɛɛtsɛ ɛ.
\v 16 Kyeea mbee melɛŋ di ebyasal ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb ɛ, etɛɛ náá, bot ɛ di esa deenek ɔ ɛpebɛka nɛ Zɛɛb.
\v 17 Mɛlyo mɔɔ ɛ ɛpebel epuud dáa pyoŋ zeni ɛgwyin ɛ. Tin, ye ɛ́ tyee wat nɛ Imenus nɛ Filɛtus,
\v 18 bɛ naazebɛka nɛ etsɛɛtsɛ. Bot binɔk eezepul ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb e bɛdhiiti bot, elyo bot ɛ náá, Zɛɛb naazeghomal bot tɔ ɛsyee.
\p 
\v 19 Bela náá epap nalyeelyel ee Zɛɛb nasum ɛ ɛpepyet ɛnyɔɛpe, mɛkpa mak ɛ kwyala kɔ tak: «Ghɛŋ nɛ gu bɔn bɛ\x - \xo 2:19 \xt Ɛla 16.5.\x*», é di'enek, «Mot di eke náá, nyɛ ɛ́ mot ɛ Ghɛŋ ɔ, nyɛ goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛliig koŋ nɛ ɛbiyo.»
\p 
\v 20 Tɔ boo ndjaa, ye ɛ́ aanàkwaazodi vɛ esaani e lɔaad nɛ yii ghwooz di esaa nɛ epata ɛ toto. Yɛ aabaadiɛ nɛ yii kpaka dɔɔ nɛ yii dyak. Bɛdhiiti kwomaa ɛ étɛp mɛbyoŋ, bɛdhiiti étɛp ɛbeaa mɛlu djas.
\v 21 Tin, mot ɛdis edhuud e mbee mɛsa mɛ etɛp binek djas ɔɔ. Mot tak ɛ aadi ɛ́ dáa esaani goŋ di ebeea dwoo mɛbyoŋ ɛ. Nyɛ eezeso nyel ɛ djas e mɛsa mɛ kukuma yɛ, e di'enek, nyɛ moo ɛ́ mbɛɛ mot, nyɛ nɛ ghwyil ɛkasa tɛtɛ esesɛɛ.
\p 
\v 22 Timote kyeea mbee egwyes e ngbaaz, kɛa tɔ epiki, nɛ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb, nɛ kwyɛl, nɛ egwyem nɛ bot ɛ di eduwal Ghɛŋ nɛ lyem wat ɔ.
\v 23 Tin, sa wɔ ààsuu mɛso nɛ etɛp di ààbɛ nɛ lo mɛsɔ ɛ, etɛɛ náá wɔ nɛ gu náá, ɛdjóo ɛ mɛwɔ.
\v 24 E di'enek, kwom mot-mɛsa ɛ Ghɛŋ ɛ ààgoka nɛ ɛdi tɔ mɛwɔ. Nyɛ goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛdi nɛ kwyɛl nɛ bot djas, nɛ ghwyil ɛlyo bot, nɛ ɛmaad ɛ lyem.
\v 25 Ye goka ɛ́ náá, nyɛ lyo bot ɛ mɛso tɔ mɛtela, nɛghu Zɛɛb ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil ɛdjɛ bɛ ɛwala dinaa bɛ waaswoola mɛfulu mɔɔ da gu etsɛɛtsɛ ɛ.
\v 26 Deenek, bɛ waabula tɔ mbɛɛ mɛfulu mɔɔ, da bɛ dus e laab ɛ Satan mot mɛkɔŋ, mot nazewa bɛ e membok étɛp bɛ neesesa mɛsa mɛ ɔ.
\c 3
\s1 Mezuk mɛ mɛlu mɛ mɛsik
\p 
\v 1 Gua ɛnyɔɛpe náá: e mɛlu mɛ mɛsik, yɛ aadi ɛ́ nɛ mɛlu mɛ di elyel ɛ.
\v 2 Etɛɛ náá, bot aanàkagwyena, bot aakadi ɛ́ elyem «tɔɔp» tɔ epata, bot ɛghɛɛa nyel, bot ɛ ɛbet, bot ɛ waabyasal Zɛɛb, bɛ aanàkaab bɛbyael bɔɔ, bot ɛ di ààmyaal bot nɛ ɛduwal etɛp dinaa ye ɛ́ e Zɛɛb ɛ.
\v 3 Bot ɛ tak aadi ɛ́, ààbɛ nɛ lyem kwyɛl, ààbɛ nɛ lyem ghoŋ, bot ɛ mɛbhekel, bot ɛ di ekwyɛ lyem ɔ, bot ɛ di nɛ lyem kyet ɔ, bot ɛ di ààkwyɛl enɛm esa.
\v 4 Bot ɛ endumta, bot ɛ di ebiyo mbɛs ɔ, bot ɛ ɛghɛɛa nyel, bɛ waakwyɛl mɛnyɔ mɛ etɛp e bɔs dhaa yii Zɛɛb.
\v 5 Bot binɔk sa tyee náá, bɛ ɛpedum koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb. Ghuna ye ɛ́ bot ɛ di ààmyaal ghwyil di tɔ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb ɛ! E di'enek, dia ɛtsetaɛpe nɛ mbi binɔk bot.
\p 
\v 6 Bɛdhiiti bot pak'ɔɔ ɛ nɛ mɛfulu mɛ ɛni tɔ mendjaa mɛ bot étɛp ɛkɔɔ boa di ààbɛ nɛ etsoŋ ɔ. Bɛ sa deenek ɛ étɛp boa tak neegwak bɛ. Boa tak ɛ, boa di àànyɔ ɛtiibal ɔ, boa ɛ di tɔ tsik mesyem ɔ, bɛ nɛ dyeebakwyɛl esa e tsik epuud di ekwyɛl ɛ djas.
\v 7 Mɛlu djas, boa tak ɛ ɛpesaa ɛgu sonok, tin, bɛ aanàkwaakogu etsɛɛtsɛ.
\v 8 Ye ɛ́ dáa bot tyee Zanɛs nɛ Zambɛlɛs nadi ebyen étɛp ɛ Moiiz ɛ, ye ɛ́ deenek ɛ bot binɔk di ebaabyen etɛp etsɛɛtsɛ. Ye ɛ́ bot ɛ mbee mɛpek dinaa ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb tokapɛ vaŋ sonok e mis mɔɔ.
\v 9 Tin, bɛ tok nɛ ghwyil ɛtɔ́ nɛ ye ɛtsetaɛpe, etɛɛ náá, bot djas ɛ waagu ewo bɔɔ, dáa yɛ Zanɛs nɛ Zambɛlɛs.
\s1 Mɛlyo mɛ mɛsik
\p 
\v 10 Yɛ kabɛ wɔy Timote ɔ, wɔ bɛ ɛ́ wɔ eegwak mɛlyo mam ɛnyɔɛpe, tɔ mɛfulu mam, tɔ mɛsa mɛ di ekwyɛl ɛ sa ɛ, tɔ ɛdum ɛ koŋ ɛ lam nɛ Zɛɛb, tɔ ɛmaad ɛ lyem'am, tɔ kwyɛl'am, nɛ tɔ zii'am,
\v 11 tɔ mɛtiiga mɛ bɛ di etiig mɛ ɛ, tɔ mezuk mam. Wɔ nɛ gu etɛp djas mɛ naboma nɛ yɛ pɛ ghaada Antiɔs ɛ, pɛ tɔ ghaada Ikoniɔm nɛ pɛ tɔ ghaada Listɛ ɛ. Wɔ nɛ gu mezuk mɛ mɛ naboma nɛ ye ɛ́. Tin, Ghɛŋ nabɛ ɛ́ nyɛ naapɛk mɛ tɔ etɛp binek djas.
\v 12 Tsɛɛtsɛ, mot djas di ekwyɛl ɛdi sosoob nɛ Zɛɛb, tɔ ɛgwakel nɛ Yezu Klisto ɔ, nyɛ waatiigaa.
\v 13 Tin, bot ɛ mbee lyem nɛ bot ɛ etsal, bɛ waatɔ́ sok tɔ embee mɛsa mɔɔ, bɛ waakɔɔ bɔɔ bɛsɔ bɔɔ. E di'enek, e mɛsik mɛ tak, bɛ waaswala kɔɔ mɛnyel mɔɔ met.
\v 14 Yɛ kabɛ wɔy ɔ, baala mɛdjek mɛ wɔ nadjek, da wɔ myaal nɛ lyem wat ɛ. Wɔ nɛ gu bɛlyoel wɔ nadjek pɛ daa lɔɔ ɔ.
\v 15 Kana edhɔma bɔ, wɔ nɛ gu ekwyala na Dɛɛ. Ye ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil ɛdjɛ wɔ etsoŋ di edjɛ mot tsik tɔ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Yezu Klisto ɛ.
\v 16 Tɔ ekwyala bɛ na Dɛɛ djas, ye ɛ́ Zɛɛb ɛ nadjɛ bot etsoŋ e ɛkwyal ɛ yɛ, ye ɛ́ nɛ boo mɛtaŋ étɛp ɛlyo bot etsɛɛtsɛ. Étɛp ɛlyaal ɛ mot ɛdjak ɛ lɛ, nɛ ɛbulal ɛ bot sa ɛbiyo ɔ e ze, dɔɔ nɛ ɛlyaal ɛ mot tsik Zɛɛb di ekwyɛl ɛ.
\v 17 Ekwyala na Dɛɛ binek ɛ, nakwyalaa ɛ etɛɛ mot-mɛsa ɛ Zɛɛb needi mot zedjala nɛ ɛsa ɛ mɛsa ɔ. Nyɛ needi mot dinaa, nyɛ ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil ɛsa membi mɛ enɛm esa djas.
\c 4
\s1 Goola Mbɛɛ Bhaadal
\p 
\v 1 Mɛ ɛpedjaala nɛ nɔ, é mis mɛ Zɛɛb nɛ é mis mɛ Yezu Klisto mot aapɛ́ɛ bot ɛ di nɛ tsik, nɛ bot ɛ zegwyɛ ɔ. Mɛ ɛpedjaala nɛ nɔ kɔ ɛsu ɛ ɛbula ɛ Yezu Klisto, nɛ kɔ ɛsu ɛ ɛyoŋ ɛ lɛ:
\v 2 wa zii tɔ ɛgoola mɛkpa mɛ Zɛɛb ye nakoozodi tɔ egwyem nɛghu tɔ ɛtap. Lyaka bɛ, dula bɛ mɛlɔ, é ghɛŋ wɔ di djɛ bɛ mɛghaaz ɛ, nɛ ɛlyo bɛ tɔ ɛdil ɛ lyem.
\v 3 Etɛɛ náá, yɛ aadi ɛ́ nɛ ɛwala dinaa bot aanàbaakwyɛl ɛgwak mbɛɛ mɛlyo ɛ. Tin, bɛ aasa e mbi bɛmɛpek djas étɛp ɛsa esa e mɛkwosak mɛ mɛnyel mɔɔ di ekwyɛl ɛ. Bɛ aadi ɛ́, nɛ bɛtɛ nɛ embee bɛlyoel aadi elyo bɛ etɛp elyem bɔɔ di ekwos ɛgwak ɛ.
\v 4 E di'enek, bɛ waabyen ɛgwak etsɛɛtsɛ, étɛp ɛdu ɛ esesa esua-sua.
\v 5 Yɛ kabɛ wɔy ɔ, sa wɔ dila lyem sok bhwoob etɛp binek djas. Maada lyem tɔ mezuk, wa zii e ɛgoola Mbɛɛ Bhaadal, silela mɛsa mɛ Zɛɛb djɛ wɔ ɛ.
\p 
\v 6 Yɛ kabɛ mam ɔ, ɛwala eezedjala ghiya yam neesee dáa buwa, ɛwala ɛmwana nɛ bɔs'ak eezedjala.
\v 7 Tin, yɛ bɛ náá, mɛ eeduu mbɛɛ tuub ɔɔ, mɛ eekɛkum pɛ ɛsik ɛ kaab mɛ na pat ɛ, mɛ eebaal ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb.
\v 8 Nenak, efute ɛpebwood mɛ etɛɛ náá, mɛ eekwak. Efute tak ɛ kɔtɔ duu, ye ɛ́ kɔtɔ mot epiki. Ye ɛ́ nyɛy Ghɛŋ mbɛɛ tetɛp ɛ kwaadjɛ mɛ dwoo mɛpɛɛa ɛ. Tin, nyɛ aanàkwaadjɛ mam ɛmet, nyɛ aadjɛ ɛ dɔɔ nɛ bot djas di egwal ɛwala nyɛ aatuula ɛ.
\s1 Mɛlyo mɛ Pɔl pɛɛ dáa Timote
\p 
\v 9 Tin, sa mɛghaaz etɛɛ náá, wɔ neeleezɛbela mɛ.
\v 10 Dhemas naazekaab mɛ, etɛɛ náá lyem tɔ kwyɛl esa e bɔs'ak. Nyɛ eetɔ́ pɛ ghaada Tesalonik. Yɛ kabɛ Kelesɔn ɔ, nyɛ eetɔ́ pɛ ghaada Ghalati. Tit naazetɔ́ yɛ pɛ ghaada Dhalmati.
\v 11 Luk nyɛ ɛmet ɛ kalik bis nɛ nɛ. E sok wɔ aazyɛ ɛ́, dha bi nɛ Malak. Etɛɛ náá, nyɛ nɛ ghwyil ɛ zɛkwyee mɛ tɔ mɛsa mɛ Zɛɛb.
\v 12 Mɛ eelwom Tisik pɛ ghaada Efɛɛz.
\v 13 E sok wɔ waazyɛ ɛ́, da wɔ zyɛ mɛ nɛ ndjookuwa yam ee mɛ nalik pɛ ghaada Toloas pɛ tɔ ndjaŋ ɛ Kalpus ɛ. Tin, da wɔ baanɔɔ mɛ mɛkana mam, daŋ-daŋ ɛ mɛkana nasael nɛ eket bɛtit.
\v 14 Deenek, Alɛkzandɛlɛ lulel egwooz nadyeebasa mɛ ɛbiyo. Tin, Ghɛŋ nyɛ ɛmet waadjɛ nyɛ efute mɛsa mɛ.
\v 15 Tin, wɔ goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛbaadi nɛ etsoŋ nɛ nɛ, etɛɛ náá nyɛ bɛ ɛ́ nyɛ dyeebasuu mɛso nɛ mɛlyo mɛ bis nadi elyo ɛ.
\p 
\v 16 Tin, mot ngɔt nabɛ ɛ́ ààkɛm e sok mɛ nadi etaŋal taŋal yam yii mɛkɛn ɛ, bot djas nakaab mɛ. Beta náá, Zɛɛb nàlaa syem tak kɔ lɔɔ.
\v 17 Tin, Ghɛŋ nakwyee mɛ, nyɛ naadjɛ mɛ mɛghaaz! Wɔ gwaa, mɛ zɛgoola Mbɛɛ Bhaadal yɛ pɛ daa bot di ààbɛ tɔ dhaad mbyak eYuda ɔ. Ghɛŋ naapɛk tɔ nuub ghee.
\v 18 Deenek, Ghɛŋ waabaapɛk mɛ tɔ embee etɛp djas. Tin, nyɛ aatsik mɛ ɛ étɛp nyɛ neeniigal mɛ tɔ ɛyoŋ ɛ lɛ di tɔ gwoo ɛ. Beta náá, duu di nɛ nɛ kɔm-kɔm sii nɛ kɔm! Ye di deenek!
\s1 Mɛswosel mɛ mɛsik
\p 
\v 19 Da wɔ ɛ́ swos Pilisil bɛ nɛ Akilas dɔɔ nɛ bot ɛ mɛbyel ɛ Onezifɔɔd.
\v 20 Elast eelik pɛ ghaada Koolɛt. Tin, mɛ eelik Tolofim pɛ ghaada Milɛ, etɛɛ náá nyel nadi ekpaa nyɛ.
\v 21 Deenek, sa mɛghaaz wɔ kum, ɛsok nɛ mbu bɛbhi nɛ kan. Ebulus, Pudɔɔ, Linus, Kolodya nɛ bɛdhiiti bɔn nyoog, bɛ eeswos wɔ.
\v 22 Beta náá, Ghɛŋ di nɛ nɔ. Beta náá enɛm nɛ embɛɛ e Zɛɛb di nɛ nen.
